Cell.Text: [S] I am the Messenger of Death. I have been bound to you by Valronis Highaire. | I am to cast judgement upon your progress throughout your journey. | Should you fail, I will appear to bring word of passing, of when the citizens of Dragon Bridge are brought to justice at the hands of the Thalmor. | What level of skill do you possess Dragonborn? Choose your challenge carefully, for the fate of Dragon Bridge's people rests on your shoulders.
[S] You have arrived at the final objective of the trial laid out before you. | But...this is not the end. You must continue your journey Dragonborn. | I will be watching over you.
